about.summary: Contains auxiliary routines for influx software. This packages is not intended to be used directly. Influx was published here: Sokol et al. (2012) <doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btr716>.

name: r-multbxxc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.0.1' %}

{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-multbxxc
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/multbxxc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/multbxxc/multbxxc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f5911f334d3390cbb7747fa6db95a7c792e74117c493acadf15752c12457e5c6

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rcpp >=1.0.0
    - r-rcpparmadillo
    - r-rmumps >=5.2.1_6
    - libblas
    - liblapack

  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-rcpp >=1.0.0
    - r-rcpparmadillo
    - r-rmumps >=5.2.1_6
    - libblas
    - liblapack

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('multbxxc')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('multbxxc')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://metasys.insa-toulouse.fr/software/influx/
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: 'Contains auxiliary routines for influx software. This packages is not intended to
    be used directly. Influx was published here: Sokol et al. (2012) <doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btr716>.'
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'
extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
     - conda-forge/r
     - sgsokol
